bodyEn:
Subject: FINAL NOTICE — Forthcoming RBI Ombudsman Complaint — Bank Charge Ref {TICKET_NO}

To: {BANK_NAME} Principal Nodal Officer,

Final notice before I file a complaint with the RBI Integrated Ombudsman (RB-IOS 2026) via https://cms.rbi.org.in within 7 days.

1. Bank charged Rs. {AMOUNT} on {TXN_DATE} (Txn ID {TXN_ID}) improperly.
2. My complaint dated {COMPLAINT_DATE}, ref {TICKET_NO}.
3. {DAYS_ELAPSED} days elapsed, no resolution.
4. Compensation claimed: Rs. {COMPENSATION_DUE} for deficiency in service, time loss, harassment.

Relief I will claim at the Ombudsman:
  • Reversal of Rs. {AMOUNT}
  • Compensation Rs. {COMPENSATION_DUE}
  • Up to Rs. 3,00,000 harassment compensation under RB-IOS 2026.

To avoid escalation, credit Rs. {AMOUNT} + Rs. {COMPENSATION_DUE} within 7 days.

Regards,
{USER_NAME}
Mobile: {MOBILE_NO}
